          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1650991614859-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>Tenderstem broccoli </strong>in half</p><p>Once the chicken has had an initial 10 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and top the potatoes with the <strong>halved Tenderstem broccoli </strong>and<strong> shallot quarters</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a further 10-12 min or until the broccoli is tender and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1650991619115-x200.jpg",
